{"tid":2479535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移民英國｜90後夫婦帶兩歲B英國住露營車　45萬買車平過租屋　游牧體驗另類教育","createTime":"2021-04-08T01:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:29:07.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28680be6c4868903098151996222c81b6e36680b","tid":2479535,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Yre8UuMrpC_-av6-UnuETLZ_F1o=/802x546/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M2NZS76UQFCOFBZLYHR6BRASE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYre8UuMrpC_-av6-UnuETLZ_F1o%3D%2F802x546%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM2NZS76UQFCOFBZLYHR6BRASE4.jpg&h=c8fff3b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疫下一家人常駐於市政府營運的露營車停車場，距離市中心不遠且安全，更有食水供應及排污設施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-h0oxVMhm1TgotmQliOjhMmweWQ=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RYFDMRLTTJGNNBTV5R77FLECVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-h0oxVMhm1TgotmQliOjhMmweWQ%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRYFDMRLTTJGNNBTV5R77FLECVE.jpg&h=ebfd0087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nO'neal以撰寫旅遊稿、當繙譯、教英文和音樂等為生，「數碼游牧」的生活方式讓他們有更多時間陪伴兒子成長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tvoU8tYlXreXreXEGbJsZtqxb6I=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LYE7KTNRZBBOZALTJ3AY4DPNYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtvoU8tYlXreXreXEGbJsZtqxb6I%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLYE7KTNRZBBOZALTJ3AY4DPNYI.jpg&h=69095e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n露營車上有一個電爐、兩個煤氣爐和一個焗爐，亦有不少儲物空間，最重要是有個大雪櫃用來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3ZbaLU-8X8nDGVS3n804bZgEfYo=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NB3SOM7C4ZHODOEYPRLGYXRPQY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3ZbaLU-8X8nDGVS3n804bZgEfYo%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNB3SOM7C4ZHODOEYPRLGYXRPQY.JPG&h=bdf8e0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二〇一九年，遊牧爸媽辭掉香港的工作，一家在紐約停留一星期，再前往拉丁美洲。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n過去十年一起遊歷70多國的90後夫婦O&rsquo;neal Choy和Janice Cheung，曾以露營車遊南美、背包遊歐洲及中南美、帶團到北韓、截順風車遊伊朗及古巴、到尼泊爾爬山，更曾在世界各地街頭賣藝。2019年，二人辭掉香港的工作，帶着當時半歲的兒子多寶出走，旅居世界，先在南美的智利、阿根廷和秘魯生活了半年，去年12月在英國買了一輛二手露營車，一邊遊歷一邊工作，體驗生活，也認識當地文化。<br />\n在英國，露營車又稱Motorhome，意即流動的家。對於29歲的O&rsquo;neal和Janice，他們的「家」亦具備基本的設備如睡床、儲物櫃、煮食爐、雪櫃、飯枱、廁所等，亦有供電、供水、通風和暖氣系統，可謂麻雀雖小，五臟俱全。<br />\n<br />\n二人都是「數碼游牧者」（Digital nomads），Janice以遙距形式從事市場營銷、網頁設計及短片製作等；自由工作者O&rsquo;neal則撰寫旅遊稿、當繙譯、教英文和音樂等。數碼游牧的生活方式讓他們有更多時間陪伴兒子成長，亦可以不時轉換居住環境，有更多機會接觸大自然，例如到公園做運動、到海邊及郊野公園散步等。夫婦倆表示，「雖然英國天氣變幻莫測，但我們風雨不改，每天都會帶兒子外出兩次。我們相信世界各地都能成為孩子的課室，旅途的經歷亦能成為教材。」由於暫時不能旅遊，他們在西南部般尼茅夫（Bournemouth）買車後，便在東南部的註冊地址肯特郡（Kent）逗留。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210408/F55W2XJPXBGFXJIT4XP5ESXJ4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210408%2FF55W2XJPXBGFXJIT4XP5ESXJ4A%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYeCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=66dc8951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210408%2FF55W2XJPXBGFXJIT4XP5ESXJ4A%2F&h=6ea43a4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210408/F55W2XJPXBGFXJIT4XP5ESXJ4A/</a>"},{"pid":"42f6b42d49b880a7f3771c4f79ca7a389e42db6b","tid":2479535,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:13:51.000Z","msg":"O&rsquo;neal 點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal